      "description": "2019 Honda Accord EX-L priced at $20,000. The engine and mechanical systems are functional but have some issues that may require attention. The interior shows noticeable wear including some staining and surface damage. The exterior has visible scratches and minor dents in several areas. Overall, this vehicle is in fair condition and is priced accordingly.",
