    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a project car or a super budget-friendly ride? This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it shows visible wear and has some mechanical issues that will need attention. That said, it's a real opportunity for a handy buyer or someone looking for the most affordable way to get mobile. Priced to reflect its condition honestly, this one's for the resourceful driver ready to put in a little TLC!",
      "price": 5500.0,
